    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0757c17"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="CN0330621T05AA">越州雲門寺</placeName><persName key="A010106">道亮</persName>傳</head><p>
<lb ed="T" n="0757c18"/><persName key="A010106">釋道亮</persName>，姓朱氏，<placeName key="CN0330602Z01AA">越州</placeName>人也。厥考前刺<placeName key="CN0330602Z02AA">會稽
    <lb ed="T" n="0757c19"/>郡</placeName><note resp="sgsz">案《浙江通志》，隋、唐八位浙江朱姓刺史、太守中，皆非越州刺史或會稽太守。</note>。<persName key="A010106">亮</persName>年八歲出家，極通經業。受具後學河
<lb ed="T" n="0757c20"/>中《三論》，復講《涅槃經》。尋入深谷，破衣覆形，
<lb ed="T" n="0757c21"/>蔬食資命，不交俗務，直守童真。<date from-iso="0705-02-25" key="j19786111978942" to-iso="0706-01-22">神龍元年</date>，
        <lb ed="T" n="0757c22"/><persName key="A002100">孝和皇帝</persName>詔<persName key="A010106">亮</persName>與法席宗師十人，入<placeName key="CN0610112A02AG">長樂大
        <lb ed="T" n="0757c23"/>內</placeName>坐夏安居。時<ref type="person" target="#A002100">帝</ref>命受菩薩戒。<persName key="A002461">睿宗</persName>及妃后
        <lb ed="T" n="0757c24"/>送異錦衾氈席。<date from-iso="0706-01-23" key="j19789431979326" to-iso="0707-02-10">二年</date>，詔於<ref type="place" target="#CN0410305A02AA">西園</ref><note resp="sgsz"><persName key="A002100">中宗</persName><date from-iso="0706-04-21" key="j19790311979060" to-iso="0706-05-20">三月</date>到<placeName key="CN0410302Z03AA">洛陽</placeName>，<date from-iso="0706-11-14" key="j19792381979267" to-iso="0706-12-13">十月</date>返<placeName key="CN0610102Z07AA">長安</placeName>。故<ref type="place" target="#CN0410305A02AA">西園</ref>可能指<placeName key="CN0410305A02AA">洛陽西苑</placeName>。</note>問道，朝廷
<lb ed="T" n="0757c25"/>欽貴。大都督<persName key="A010118">李孝逸</persName>、工部尚書<persName key="A010116">張錫</persName>、國子監
        <lb ed="T" n="0757c26"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>周</sic><corr>司</corr></choice>業<persName key="A010112">崔融</persName><note resp="sgsz"><date from-iso="0706-01-23" key="j19789431979326" to-iso="0707-02-10">神龍二年</date>，<persName key="A010112">崔融</persName>以國子司業卒於任。《景德傳燈錄》《傳法正宗記》《五燈全書目錄》《禪燈世譜》皆查無<persName>周業</persName>其人，應為「司業」之誤。</note>、祕書監<persName key="A008710">賀知章</persName>、<placeName key="CN0330182Z08AA">睦州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A010832">康<add resp="sgsz">希</add>詵</persName>，同
<lb ed="T" n="0757c27"/>心慕仰，請問禪心，多結師資，或傳香火。卒
<lb ed="T" n="0757c28"/>年八十二，門人<persName key="A010110">慧遠</persName>等建塔，<persName key="A007959">萬齊融</persName>為《銘》紀
<lb ed="T" n="0757c29"/>述。</p>
